bug.author: rkuester
bug.summary: micro: in CONTRIBUTING.md, the path a test script is wrong
bug.description:
<denchmark-link:https://github.com/orgs/tensorflow/teams/micro>@tensorflow/micro</denchmark-link>
Tensorflow version (commit SHA if source): 556fa12
In micro's CONTRIBUTING.md, the path to a script to run tests prior to submitting a PR uses (what is now, at least) an invalid path.
tensorflow/tensorflow/lite/micro/CONTRIBUTING.md
Lines 204 to 208 in 7958e0c
1. Run all the tests for x86, and any other platform that you are modifying.
```
tensorflow/lite/micro/tools/make/tools/ci_build/test_x86.sh
```
The fix is trivial and on its way.
